-- Chrysler to offer $1,000 gift certificates to customers: report
-- 
-- Thu May 14, 2009 11:12pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/05/15/us-chrysler-idUSTRE54E0KG20090515

 

 (Reuters) - Chrysler Holding LLC is preparing to send all existing customers certificates good for $1,000 toward purchase of new vehicles according to The Wall Street Journal. 

